# Generated documentation
docs/_build/
docs/build/

# ===== END OF GITIGNORE =====

# ===== NOTES =====
# 
# To add your own wallpapers without committing them:
# 1. Create a local 'wallpapers' directory
# 2. Add your images there
# 3. Update hyprpaper.conf with local paths
# 4. The wallpapers/ directory is ignored by default
#
# To add personal scripts:
# 1. Create scripts with '-personal' or '-private' suffix
# 2. These will be ignored automatically
#
# To backup your current configs before applying these:
# cp -r ~/.config/hypr ~/.config/hypr-backup
# cp -r ~/.config/waybar ~/.config/waybar-backup
# etc.
